# Browser Icon Placeholder
# This is a placeholder for the browser icon file
# You should replace this with an actual PNG icon file (256x256 pixels)
# The icon should represent security and browsing
# Recommended colors: Blue (#2563eb), Dark (#0f172a), White (#ffffff)
# Design suggestions: Shield with browser window, lock icon, or security symbol

# To create your icon:
# 1. Use a design tool like Canva, Figma, or Photoshop
# 2. Create a 256x256 PNG image
# 3. Use security-themed colors and symbols
# 4. Save as browser-icon.png in this directory
# 5. The icon will be used for the browser window and taskbar

# Temporary: You can use any PNG file as placeholder
# The browser will still work without the icon
